snippet.title: The Garden Path: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wander down the Garden Path. Available now on Steam(PC) and Nintendo Switch.
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1638500/The_Garden_Path/
Nintendo eShop: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/the-garden-path-switch/

The Garden Path is a slice-of-life gardening sim that celebrates small moments. No matter how you decide to play, the garden is a tender world of familiar sights and sounds, mysteries, and friendly faces. A space to call your own, to curate, and to reflect.  A wonderful and wistful adventure awaits when wandering The Garden Path.
